{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"一个工人的话","authors":["胡维新"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":2,"day":26}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个工人的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡维新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个被服匠的儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是被压迫的阶级。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是老财资本家的天下："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看咱穷人一钱不值，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简直是有钱人的牛马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会说话的工具。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"☆　☆　☆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹爹一身好技术，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啥也没挣下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便宜了资本家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来，爹死娘嫁人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活更无法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人家还说我“命里活该”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“穷窝里生不出富娃娃”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我啥时候也争口气……”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有这个思想可不敢提，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧社会里咱哪能扬眉吐气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪有穷人说话的余地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"☆　☆　☆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我自从参加了革命工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才找到了自己的家乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见到了爹娘——共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我穿上工人服，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我脱下破衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推去污垢的乱发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露出了人模样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里有民主没有剥削，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有互助没有忌妒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅真心教学员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学员诚意爱师傅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"☆　☆　☆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我刚来时“傻”的可怜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么本领也没有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党培养我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教育我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来没嫌过麻烦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教我技术，教我写算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还说：“别想家，好好干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将来当个英雄汉！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂就是我的家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还想啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十几年来我在工厂长大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"☆　☆　☆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树枝儿长大忘不了根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党抚养我长大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我忘不了呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要永远记在心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要努力生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把蒋匪消灭完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫全国工人兄弟见青天。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}